name: OISHII DESU! ｜ This is Delicious!
description:
美味しい｜oishii｜delicious｜sedap
2000 x 2000 px MP4 with Audio (loopable)
Edition of 20

「この動画を見ながら食事すると、どんな食べ物でも美味しくなるよ。」
「kono douga minagara shokuji suru to, donnna tabemono demo oishikunaru yo. 」
「Watching this animation while eating, will make whatever you’re eating, delicious.」

This animation is a remix of what was originally made as GIF instagram stamp. The Oishii stamp has garnered 9 million views by Oct 2021, and went to become Gengoya’s most used GIF stamp, stamped on top of lots and lots of food-related stories.
Music by MusMus.
